                  <msItem>
                     <p> Convention dated on the day of the Nativity of St. John the <pb n="408"/> Baptist,
               <origDate notBefore="1300-11-20" notAfter="1301-11-19">29 Ed. I</origDate>, by which <persName nymRef="Mortun">
                           <forename>Michael</forename>
                        </persName> and <persName>
                           <forename>Walter</forename> de <surname>Morton</surname>
                        </persName>, the lords, grant to
               <persName>
                           <forename>Robert</forename>, son of <persName>
                              <forename>Hugh</forename> de <surname>Orsolooue</surname>
                           </persName>
                        </persName>, 
               common pasture in the fee of <placeName key="place_108521">Morton</placeName> for all kinds of animals, as
               marked by boundaries (which are specified) for 25 years, paying 6d. annually, and
               giving 20s. for entrance. 
               . </p>
